<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长坐在市政府的办公室里。电话响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是时候了！”电话里的声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，老板。”布洛姆市长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挂断了电话。市长走进另外一个房间，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>打开保险箱，从里面拿出一大笔钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”秘书说，“您在干什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这笔钱是用来修建美罗城游乐场的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长一句话不说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把钱塞进一个公文包里走掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望新的游乐场能有一个大堡垒。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有桥、梯子、滑梯和隧道！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们正在美罗城公园里玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们站在满是杂草的空地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>新的游乐场将在这里建成。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望游乐场里有一座塔！” 特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想要一个秋千。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“荡秋千让我觉得好像在飞。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔用怀疑的眼神看着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望游乐场早点建好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉说，“我等得不耐烦了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们早应该让火箭女孩儿帮忙来建的。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她很快就会建好的。”罗西转了转眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得火箭女孩儿有更重要的事情去做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔叹了一口气。“你说得对。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他眼睛一亮，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们知道怎样才最酷吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎样？”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果有两个火箭女孩儿就最好了！”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个跟坏人斗争，另一个帮我们修建游乐场！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都笑了。罗西摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特勒尔，这是我听过的最可笑的想法了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔耸耸肩。"我只是说说而已。那会很酷。"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表轻轻地响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西避开朋友，按下了手表上的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯先生的脸出现在屏幕上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊-哈！”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“史密斯侦探不知道我的真实身份！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西迅速戴上她的面具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“史密斯侦探。”她小声问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗？布洛姆市长在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯清了清嗓子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有麻烦了，火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长好像偷走了修建美罗城游乐场的钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西愣住了。“不可能。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长不可能干那样的事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道很难让人相信。”史密斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是他的秘书亲眼看到的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望你马上来市政府。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西眼咽了咽口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，侦探先生。我马上就到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>